Apart from his legendary career, a great advocate of civil rights, environmental protection and independent cinema, an opponent of the drifting off Hollywood, is now also going there.
We have probably often seen him stand by foot in bowls full of vinaigrette, in sauces, pastries or other foods, and thought this to be quite tasteless, although we found it funny at first.
